snippet.title: Lemmings: Amstrad CPC (1992)
snippet.description:
Intro and gameplay from Lemmings on the Amstrad CPC, released in 1992.
Developed by Walking Circles and published by Psygnosis.

Game credits:
- Adrian Powell - Painting
- 'Walking Circles' - Code, Graphics 
- Tony Williams - Music

Watch other editions of the Lemmings game here:
https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLW_a1Ic-Y4n_sYe2n1OCwe0j03EOxxq3U

Enjoy the video? Remember to like, comment and subscribe to Retro Gaming TV - http://bit.ly/2N5gjMA
